{"abstract": "Outrage at the very wealthy may be impeding a national discussion of how to raise the living standards of the bottom 20 percent, an economist writes.", "web_url": "https://www.nytimes.com/2014/03/09/business/a-top-heavy-focus-on-income-inequality.html", "snippet": "Outrage at the very wealthy may be impeding a national discussion of how to raise the living standards of the bottom 20 percent, an economist writes.", "lead_paragraph": "I worry about growing income inequality. But I worry even more that the discussion is too narrowly focused. I worry that our outrage at the top 1 percent is distracting us from the problem that we should really care about: how to create opportunities and ensure a reasonable standard of living for the bottom 20 percent. ", "print_section": "BU", "print_page": "4", "source": "The New York Times", "multimedia": [{"rank": 0, "subtype": "xlarge", "caption": null, "credit": null, "type": "image", "url": "images/2014/03/09/business/9-VIEW/9-VIEW-articleLarge.jpg", "height": 600, "width": 600, "subType": "xlarge", "crop_name": "articleLarge", "legacy": {"xlarge": "images/2014/03/09/business/9-VIEW/9-VIEW-articleLarge.jpg", "xlargewidth": 600, "xlargeheight": 600}}, {"rank": 0, "subtype": "jumbo", "caption": null, "credit": null, "type": "image", "url": "images/2014/03/09/business/9-VIEW/9-VIEW-jumbo.jpg", "height": 1024, "width": 1024, "subType": "jumbo", "crop_name": "jumbo", "legacy": {}}, {"rank": 0, "subtype": "superJumbo", "caption": null, "credit": null, "type": "image", "url": "images/2014/03/09/business/9-VIEW/9-VIEW-superJumbo.jpg", "height": 2048, "width": 2048, "subType": "superJumbo", "crop_name": "superJumbo", "legacy": {}}, {"rank": 0, "subtype": "thumbnail", "caption": null, "credit": null, "type": "image", "url": "images/2014/03/09/business/9-VIEW/9-VIEW-thumbStandard.jpg", "height": 75, "width": 75, "subType": "thumbnail", "crop_name": "thumbStandard", "legacy": {"thumbnail": "images/2014/03/09/business/9-VIEW/9-VI